OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of patchy light rain
OL,7,Fand drizzle at times across northern
OL,8,Fparts of the region this evening and
OL,9,Fovernight. Low cloud, mist and murk
OL,10,Fmoving into western coasts, with some
OL,11,Fhill fog. A mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA grey start, but cloud slowly
OL,14,Flifting through the day. Some warm
OL,15,Fbright or occasional sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping into the afternoon,
OL,17,Fparticularly in the south. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
